-803173779.text: "Taken together, our data suggest that VES induces activation of PKC and PKC dependent hypophosphorylation of retinoblastoma protein, which results in induction of apoptosis, and that VES induced early activation of ERK and ERK dependent induction of p21 (WAF1) are not required for apoptosis."
